---
layout: layouts/base.njk
---
<section class="hero hero-split">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <h1>Welcome to my website!</h1>
    <p>My name is Jón Ingi Hlynsson and I am a licensed psychologist and PhD researcher trained to dissect minds, models, and methods — running on <em>precision, caffeine, and contempt for sloppy psychometrics</em>.</p>
    <p>This site is a central hub for the various projects I am associated with, and a "low-stakes" creative outlet to keep practicing my writing — hence the <a href="/blog/">blog</a>.</p>
    <p class="credential">Licensed psychologist since June 2025 — <a href="/assets/wp/2025-06-Jon_Hlynsson-embaetti-starfsleyf-30-06-2025.pdf">view licence (PDF)</a></p>
    <div class="hero-links">
      <a href="{{ site.linkedin }}">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="{{ site.instagram }}">Instagram</a>
      <a href="/feed.xml">RSS</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <img class="hero-portrait" src="/assets/wp/2025-04-8518a47e-a243-4c3d-bc4a-0e13a5e740f5-1.png" alt="Jón Ingi Hlynsson" width="320" height="320" loading="eager">
</section>

<h2 class="section-label">Latest writing</h2>
<ul class="post-list">
  {% for post in collections.posts | head(5) %}
  <li>
    <span class="post-meta"><time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time></span>
    <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
    <p>{{ post.data.description or (post.templateContent | excerpt) }}</p>
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
<a class="all-posts-link" href="/blog/">All posts →</a>
